		</div>
		<div class = "firstYear">
			<h1> JUNIOR YEAR </h1>
			<p> During the junior year, Media Fellows take part in a <strong>semester-long, full-credit professional internship</strong> in a media setting such as a newspaper, entertainment program or public relations office.</p>
